Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: John Cage, Wilbur Mills and Oliver Franks
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00ylfr3
Last Broadcast Date: New Year's Day 1993
A look back at the lives of the notable figures to die in 1992, including composer John Cage, politician Wilbur Mills and British Ambassador Oliver Franks.